MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a fault with the power in the LL65 postcode area of Holyhead. This is causing flickering  supply to a number of properties. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at  10:42PM Our next available engineer will attend site to investigate and our team will work to get your power back to normal as quickly and as safely as possible. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 10:59PM on 12th March 2021
